lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps, one of the world's most recognisable athletes, will lead a crop of new faces to Rio as a week of ruthless competition at the U.S. Olympic trials ended on Sunday and shifted the focus to the Summer Games pool.

headline.main: Analysis-Phelps Leads Newcomers on Road to Rio
